# Build context for frontend/Dockerfile, backend/Dockerfile, etc. (context: repo root).
# Excluding node_modules prevents COPY from replacing the image's `yarn install` tree with the
# host's — mixed hoisting / OS can cause ENOENT (e.g. tough-cookie v5 paths vs v6 layout).

**/node_modules

**/.next
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results

.git
.gitignore
.cursor

**/.env
**/.env.local

*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
